snippet.title: Giraffe and Annika（ジラフとアンニカ） - Announcement Trailer (Upcoming Indie Game on Steam) 2019
snippet.description:
••► Release Date : 2019
••► Developer / Publisher : Atelier Mimina / Sony Music Entertainment (Japan) Inc. / UNTIES
••► Steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1122100/Giraffe__Annika/

==========

Lovable cat-eared Annika sets off on a grand quest on the Island of Spica! 3D adventure & rhythm action mesh in the lush, pastoral and beatuful manga-spired world of Giraffe & Annika!

==========
